text: I liked this movie, it grapples with some very relevant and important questions.  I am now a completely transparent person online by choice.  I became that way because I was being cyber-stalked and cell phone spied upon by some obsessed crazy person. Getting my privacy back was apparently not an option. I prefer having witnesses of other people to just him knowing everything about me.  The loss of privacy is devastating and can never be restored.  Tis a gift to be simple, tis a gift to be free.
